text: Sean Rodriguez Marquette (born June 30, 1988) is an American actor. He is best known for being Johnny Atkins in The Goldbergs and Schooled, and for voicing Mac in the Cartoon Network series Foster's Home for Imaginary Friends from 2004 to 2009. ==Life and career== His brother Chris is an actor. His father is Cuban. He made his acting debut on television in the soap opera series All My Children in 1995 as Jamie Martin. ==Other websites== * Category:1988 births Category:Actors from Dallas Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:American child actors
